Ayo!

00:10:05.240 --> 00:10:06.280
Maafkan kami, Nona.

00:10:06.400 --> 00:10:08.880
Kami tidak memiliki izin
untuk melayani Anda.

00:10:09.160 --> 00:10:11.200
Hei tunggu..

00:10:11.280 --> 00:10:12.320
Hei, apa ini..

00:10:12.440 --> 00:10:17.240
Kakak ipar Radha, Anda
dengan hormat mengundang kami.

00:10:17.320 --> 00:10:19.360
